results.title: Resurrect Animate Seduce Rainbow Glittery Wall Sign
results.description:
These are not times for "Live Laugh Love" and this parody has been bouncing around in my brain.  

Watching a lot of vampire, witch, and zombie movies lately?  Bingeing Chilling Adventures of Sabrina or Buffy?  Counting the days until the next Walking Dead episode?  Rereading all of the Anita Blake sseries (or maybe even Twilight)?  This sign is for you.  Sassy, silly, and super sparkly.  

Rainbow silver glitter lettering with the words "Resurrect Animate Seduce" on a midlight blue background with charcoal gray frame.  A perfect gift for a goth friend, witchy sister, or anyone who needs a dark laugh.  Hang it over your altar, bath tub, or wherever you go to hide from your family when you need a break and a little magical escapism.  

The glittery quote is hard to capture on camera, but SO sparkly in person.
